N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4603.4 - Time when copies must be received by commission

State Regulations

One copy of the findings and determination for games of
chance license, together with a copy of the application, must be received by
the commission at least five days prior to the holding of the first game
authorized. Notes
